<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.hdot.org/">Holocaust Denial On Trial: Holocaust Denial and the 2000 Libel Trial in the U.K.</a>, a project of The Rabbi Donald A. Tam Institute for Jewish Studies at <a href="/wiki/Emory_University" title="Emory University">Emory University</a>.</li>
